=== 家人被绑架 ===

2016年3月19日，长平在德国之声的"长平观察"专栏在没有实际证据的情况下，发表了题为《[[贾葭|贾葭]]失踪，睁眼之罪》的评论文章，关注中国媒体人贾葭被中国当局认为与一封《要求习近平同志辞去党和国家领导职务》的公开信有关而"神秘失踪"后，国内的家人和亲属遭到中国警方的广泛调查和骚扰威胁，两个弟弟和一个妹妹于3月27日被警方"绑架"（指没有任何法律手续的拘押） <ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.dw.com/zh/dw%E4%B8%93%E6%A0%8F%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E9%95%BF%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%9B%A0%E5%85%B6%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%B1%E8%B8%AA/a-19145600 | title = "DW专栏作者长平家人因其评论“被失踪”" | accessdate = 2016-03-27 | archive-date = 2019-10-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191029124717/https://www.dw.com/zh/dw%E4%B8%93%E6%A0%8F%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E9%95%BF%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%9B%A0%E5%85%B6%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%B1%E8%B8%AA/a-19145600 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。警察利用亲情关系要求长平停止批评中共，遭到长平公开拒绝，并曝光其谈判详情，切断与家人联系。此事成为国际媒体焦点。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://cn.nytimes.com/china/20160329/c29china/ | title = "旅德作家长平称家人因公开信事件被扣押" | accessdate = 2016-03-29 | archive-date = 2019-04-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190414080706/https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20160329/c29china/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>3月29日，长平家人得以取保候审。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://cn.nytimes.com/opinion/20160417/c17inyt-edchang/ | title = "我为什么拒绝与中国政府交易" | accessdate = 2016-04-17 | archive-date = 2021-05-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210505151122/https://cn.nytimes.com/opinion/20160417/c17inyt-edchang/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://theinitium.com/article/20160408-parenting-letters-chagnping/|title=長平 : 請別害怕給孩子解釋政治|publisher=端传媒|date=2015-10-27|access-date=2020-11-12|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112201247/https://theinitium.com/article/20160408-parenting-letters-chagnping/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

